{"tid":614194,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[中出即飛] 張振朗陳芷尤分手 不涉第三者","createTime":"2018-04-02T10:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T11:41:33.000Z","uid":117837,"like":6,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"0e7bfc585d20d57bb15e69605e7111df4920ff79","tid":614194,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"張振朗同陳芷尤拍拖多時，今日齊齊喺社交網站貼文宣佈分手：「多謝這幾年來的美好回憶，所有事情就像昨天發生一樣，依舊溫暖。我們當中並沒有涉及第三者。雖然現在關係有所改變，但我們都會在遠方繼續支持大家。感謝這幾年來對我們的關心。」而陳芷尤回覆傳媒查詢指二人已經分開了一段時間，分手原因是大 家各有各忙以及觀念不同。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180402/large/1522657163_e71c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180402%2Flarge%2F1522657163_e71c.png&h=01e45067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180402/large/1522657166_59bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180402%2Flarge%2F1522657166_59bb.jpg&h=80547bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180402/large/1522657175_6d9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180402%2Flarge%2F1522657175_6d9b.jpg&h=859e423a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180402/large/1522657172_5a36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180402%2Flarge%2F1522657172_5a36.jpg&h=c3649e85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年他們孖公仔到歐洲玩樂，當時被網民捕獲之後，張振朗回覆傳媒話「我們玩得非常開心」間接承認女友地位，而他們今日所張貼的照片，相信就是他們到歐洲旅遊時的照片。二人相識於第25期訓練班，即使他們多次拍拖被人斷正，但張振朗及陳芷尤都異口同聲以「好好朋友」稱呼對方。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20180402/579804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20180402%2F579804&d=oJJwycnxtbbIxqRg37QJgcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c1da3dd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20180402%2F579804&h=cc748fdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20180402/579804</a>"},{"pid":"18ae1e2e2c2065ab791b5e0cd1a3064ecba86d8d","tid":614194,"uid":36478,"like":234,"dislike":7,"score":227,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0cb5f45d441d4a49f5405ce2feba6f8e97c729","tid":614194,"uid":32723,"like":59,"dislike":3,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"條仔上位就勒令分手.<br />\n<br />\n炒作下先., 轉玩地下情<br />\n<br />\n跟住同同劇既PARTNER 扮拍拖又炒作,."},{"pid":"370ba0f6c785174e9aa9122c75c592613e18bab5","tid":614194,"uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩"},{"pid":"06971d62bfb985b0ff20afc9262b226c9fe114aa","tid":614194,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:17:37.000Z","msg":"想分手博新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe04958ce2cc237eae35c7dbebbca7f36b728c6e","tid":614194,"uid":71824,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"張振朗有乜位上? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8470733da41e10afc5a9765eb3cf1657cba210f2","tid":614194,"uid":117837,"like":67,"dislike":14,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20120706/large/18ed9p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%